ideal for last mile e-commerce operations, general distribution and flex operations and occupiers needing an updated facility to promote their business and operations
75 State is perfectly positioned to accommodate corporate users aiming to attract top-notch talent in a First Class business environment
Close to retail and public recreational amenities
